OL,3,CBishop says he 'can totally get why
OL,4,Ctrust' is so low following recent
OL,5,Cscandals
OL,7,FA Bishop has said that recent scandals
OL,8,Fregarding the Church of England has
OL,9,Fcaused "huge reputational damage" but
OL,10,Fwill ultimately "purify" the church.
OL,12,FPhilip North has been the Bishop of
OL,13,FBlackburn since 2023, and at a
OL,14,Fbriefing by the Religion Media Centre
OL,15,Fhe said he "can totally get why trust
OL,16,Fin bishops is at such a low ebb".
