OL,5,Cscandals
OL,7,FThe Church of England has been mired
OL,8,Fby a number of scandals over the last
OL,9,Ffew months, with Justin Welby
OL,10,Fresigning as archbishop of Canterbury
OL,11,Fin November, while his temporary stand-
OL,12,Fin Archbishop of York Stephen Cottrell
OL,13,Fis also facing calls to quit.
OL,15,FOn Thursday 30 January, John
OL,16,FPerumbalath resigned as the Bishop of
OL,17,FLiverpool following multiple sexual
OL,18,Fassault and harassment allegations
OL,19,Fwhich were made against him.
