OL,3,CBishop says he 'can totally get why
OL,4,Ctrust' is so low following recent
OL,5,Cscandals
OL,7,FBishop Perumbalath continues to deny
OL,8,Fthe allegations, but retired to avoid
OL,9,Fthe issue being "a distraction" and
OL,10,Fclaimed a "trial by media" had made it
OL,11,Fimpossible for him to continue in his
OL,12,Frole.
OL,14,FOne of the complainants, who alleged
OL,15,Fthe harassment allegations, identified
OL,16,Fherself as the Bishop of Warrington,
OL,17,FBeverley Mason.
OL,19,FIn a statement she called it a
OL,20,F"biblical imperative" that "a bishop
OL,21,Fcannot be above the law".
