OL,7,FThe Archbishop of York Stephen
OL,8,FCottrell became involved in the
OL,9,Fscandal when it was alleged by Channel
OL,10,F4 News that he bullied members of a
OL,11,Fcommittee to secure John Perumbalath's
OL,12,Fappointment as the Bishop of
OL,13,FLiverpool. Both the Archbishop and the
OL,14,FChurch of England "categorically
OL,15,Freject" these allegations.
