OL,3,CBishop says he 'can totally get why
OL,4,Ctrust' is so low following recent
OL,5,Cscandals
OL,7,FSpeaking about the scandals, the
OL,8,FBishop of Blackburn Philip North said:
OL,9,F"I can't deny there is huge
OL,10,Freputational damage done to the church
OL,11,Fat a national level, to the standing
OL,12,Fof bishops and to the perception of
OL,13,Fthe Church in the Church of England,
OL,14,Fand we feel still to be very much on
OL,15,Fthe back foot, very much on the
OL,16,Fdefensive."
OL,18,FHe described the Church at a local
OL,19,Flevel as remaining "credible" and
OL,20,F"still vibrant".
