OL,3,CBishop says he 'can totally get why
OL,4,Ctrust' is so low following recent
OL,5,Cscandals
OL,7,FBut he added: "I think, speaking as a
OL,8,Fbishop, we've got some work to do to
OL,9,Frecover trust, and certainly I feel
OL,10,Fless confident in speaking to the
OL,11,Fpublic square than I did last year."
OL,13,FGiving examples, he said he feels less
OL,14,Fconfident in speaking out on some
OL,15,Fissues around justice and poverty.
OL,17,FBishop Philip North said it felt like
OL,18,Fthe Church was "being purified" by the
OL,19,Frecent scandals, and "God is working
OL,20,Fthrough this... media frenzy".
