OL,7,FThe General Synod, otherwise known as
OL,8,Fthe Church's parliament, will debate
OL,9,Fand vote on a new model on
OL,10,Fsafeguarding next week.
OL,12,FAlex Frost, a Synod member and vicar
OL,13,Fin Burnley, described the Church's
OL,14,Fhierarchy as being "in disarray".
OL,16,FHe said: "I think locally people are
OL,17,Fvery keen to just get on with the job
OL,18,Fin hand.
