OL,7,F"I think we're kind of running two
OL,8,Fparallel universes here ` we're
OL,9,Frunning the hierarchy of the Church of
OL,10,FEngland that is in disarray, and we've
OL,11,Fgot the local churches that are going
OL,12,Fabout their day-to-day ministry, doing
OL,13,Ftheir best against the backdrop of a
OL,14,Fchurch that seems to be in free fall."
